              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Potassium dihydrogen phosphate, sulfur and sodium",
                "chloride were used as the targets to determine the",
                "thick-target yields of 34mCl on phosphorus, sulfur and",
                "chlorine. All irradiation samples were pressed into",
                "smooth-surfaced pellets of 1 cm in diameter by using an",
                "oil pressure press of 10 tons. The thickness of each",
                "pellet was thick enough to stop the incident alpha",
                "particles. All pellets prepared were wrapped with",
                "10 mu-m aluminum foil of more than 99.99% purity."
              ]
            }
          ],
